articles.description: Some additional details about the site
articles.contents: This site is meant to be a collection of informative resources that I read centered largely around Machine Learning. Material on this site is constantly being updated. For a lot of articles (especially coursework related), there are PDFs that are attached as well (on the right side of the margin at the start of the article).
